## STEP 1 VERIFICATION CHECKLIST — MANDATORY

**Before proceeding to Step 2, confirm ALL of the following:**

### Color Verification
- [ ] Every color has a **specific element** noted (not just "hero bg" — which element?)
- [ ] Accent colors specify **exact text** they appear on
- [ ] RGB values converted to HEX (use `rgb_to_hex` function)
- [ ] No estimated colors — all from DevTools

### Typography Verification  
- [ ] **Line height measured** for every element — no blank entries
- [ ] **Font family noted** for H1 (serif vs sans-serif matters)
- [ ] **Font weight verified** — don't assume, check DevTools
- [ ] Text color specifies **which color token** it uses

### Layout Verification
- [ ] **Section padding** measured from border to first/last element
- [ ] **Card styles** documented (border, radius, shadow)
- [ ] **Button styles** for EVERY button type (primary, outline, nav CTA)

### Element Inventory
- [ ] **Navigation scanned** — all links, logo, CTA button
- [ ] **Icons flagged** — count them, note they're skipped
- [ ] **Forms checked** — confirm none exist or note if skipped
- [ ] **Images noted** — which are placeholders vs skipped

### Cross-Check Against DOM
- [ ] **Snapshot reviewed** — does DOM match my section breakdown?
- [ ] **Text content verified** — exact copy from browser, not memory
- [ ] **Widget types mapped** — heading vs text-editor decisions made

**If any checkbox is unchecked, STOP. Go back and measure.**

